						<p>Chōḻa, Rājakēsarivarman, 19th year = c. 10th Century.</p>						

						<p>Gift of land, made tax-free, for a lamp and offerings, by a Brāhmaṇa lady of Timmikuḍi who built the shrine of Ādittabhaṭṭārakar on the hill.</p>						

